metadata.name: BATTLES-1
metadata.description:
The first of seven battles

The collection of paintings "Seven Battles" narrates a part of my life.
Each of us has been the observer, the subject and the object of such confrontations ...
Female-male coexistence, confrontation of feminine elegance and fragility against male gladiatorial organs.

Owner of this NFT will receive the Original painting *
Oil painting on canvas   110x73cm

"See the image and edition information of this NFT on my website"
